<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Dimitris Glezos' old personal site - Mini-post</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/weblog/feeds/tag/mini-post.atom" rel="self"></link><id>https://dimitris.glezos.com/</id><updated>2009-11-08T00:00:00+02:00</updated><entry><title>Today’s exploration: Beauty</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/11/08/todays-exploration-beauty/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-11-08T00:00:00+02:00</published><updated>2009-11-08T00:00:00+02:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-11-08:/weblog/2009/11/08/todays-exploration-beauty/</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;“In its most profound sense, beauty may engender a salient experience of positive reflection about the meaning of one’s own existence.” [&lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beauty"&gt;article&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="http://ow.ly/AqCE"&gt;video&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Quotes"></category><category term="Thoughts"></category></entry><entry><title>Quote: On Teams</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/10/29/quote-on-teams/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-10-29T00:00:00+02:00</published><updated>2009-10-29T00:00:00+02:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-10-29:/weblog/2009/10/29/quote-on-teams/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;“I enjoy a working environment where the word ‘team’ is uttered in derision, and view the process of team or community as a result of mutual respect and enlightened self interest as opposed to a management method where fuzzy feelings are elicited to get the benefits and delegate the blame …&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;“I enjoy a working environment where the word ‘team’ is uttered in derision, and view the process of team or community as a result of mutual respect and enlightened self interest as opposed to a management method where fuzzy feelings are elicited to get the benefits and delegate the blame.” (comment by dkite on &lt;a href="http://lwn.net/Articles/359013/"&gt;LWN article&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Quotes"></category></entry><entry><title>Skype wows</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/10/14/skype-wows/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-10-14T00:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2009-10-14T00:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-10-14:/weblog/2009/10/14/skype-wows/</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Calling to Greek landline phones (both in-town and country-wide) is cheaper with Skype than Forthnet. Yay for N900 handling all my local calls then.&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Random"></category></entry><entry><title>Greetings.</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/09/22/greetings/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-09-22T00:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2009-09-22T00:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-09-22:/weblog/2009/09/22/greetings/</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;“To the past, or to the future. To an age when thought is free. From the Age of Big Brother, from the Age of the Thought Police, from a dead man… greetings.” (&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Am3ojIKYYrQ"&gt;1984&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Quotes"></category></entry><entry><title>Rock Paper Scissors Spock Lizard</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/09/21/rock-paper-scissors-spock-lizard/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-09-21T00:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2009-09-21T00:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-09-21:/weblog/2009/09/21/rock-paper-scissors-spock-lizard/</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;“Scissors cuts Paper covers Rock crushes Lizard poisons Spock smashes Scissors decapitates Lizard eats Paper disproves Spock vaporizes Rock crushes Scissors.” (via @mperedim)&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Random"></category><category term="Tech/web"></category></entry><entry><title>Life colors</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/09/19/life-colors/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-09-19T00:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2009-09-19T00:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-09-19:/weblog/2009/09/19/life-colors/</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;“The friends of mine paint with a black color. Because you wasted their red.” (&lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-1twb1bQpQ"&gt;magic de spell&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Quotes"></category><category term="Thoughts"></category></entry><entry><title>Maemo Summit</title><link href="https://dimitris.glezos.com/weblog/2009/09/19/maemo-summit/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-09-19T00:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2009-09-19T00:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>Dimitris Glezos</name></author><id>tag:dimitris.glezos.com,2009-09-19:/weblog/2009/09/19/maemo-summit/</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Yeehaa! I’m going to the &lt;a href="http://maemo.org/news/events/maemo_summit_2009/"&gt;Maemo Summit&lt;/a&gt; baby! Amsterdam, long time no see! #maesum&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="random"></category><category term="Mini-post"></category><category term="Personal"></category><category term="Tech/web"></category></entry><entry>